data.description: Charming 3bedroom,2.5 bathroom townhome within the community of Isola, this two-story townhome offers both space and functionality, making it an ideal choice for those seeking comfort.  Upon entry, you're welcomed into an inviting living space. The open-concept design seamlessly connects the living, dining, and kitchen areas, making it perfect for entertaining or relaxing with family.   Upstairs, you'll discover three generously sized bedrooms. The master suite complete with an en-suite bathroom. The other two bedrooms share a bathroom, ensuring comfort and convenience for all occupants. Furthermore, this townhome offers the convenience of a laundry room on the upper level, making chores a breeze. A private patio or backyard space provides a tranquil area to unwind. Showings by appt only!!
